name: DREAM BANGKOK
description: Cityscape night view of Bangkok city among the stars and the Milky Way. What a beautiful and wonderful sight, but in reality it is difficult to see or photograph the stars and the Milky Way in the city because it is obscured by the city lights. so It was born as a surreal photography work. This work came up to remind that. Beautiful is always around us but sometimes because of something like civilization. So we can't see it.
